<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngai diu kingkang sang-za gi chuh,
 Pahchakna la a sau ie;
 Isun vaihawm, van a kipak,
 Hehpih Lalpan vai a hawm.

[V2]
 En in, van chutphah a chu'n,
 Isun vannuoi vai A hawm;
 Hallelujah, Hallelujah;
 Isun vannuoi vai A hawm.

[V3]
 2. Leng lopi'n kumsawt in vaihawm,
 Lalna cheng nanga ahi;
 Na lungsiet 'pat khenthei umlo,
 Nanga dinga Na siemte.

[V4]
 Na zahngaihna lim nuoiah;
 Na mel hawih chuh mu dingin!
 Hallelujah; Hallelujah,
 Na mel hawih chuh mu dingin.

[V5]
 3. Hukdampa hung kilang mengin,
 Ni lopi chuh hun tunin;
 Sapna aw lauhum git tiengleh,
 Lei leh van taimang ina.

[V6]
 Sana kingkang tawh la sa'n,
 &quot;Lopi Lalpen Lopi hen;
 Hallelujah; Hallelujah
 Lopi Lalpen lopi hen.&quot;</lyrics>
<title>HARK! TEN THOUSAND HARPS AND VOICES</title>
<hymn_number>137</hymn_number>
</song>